{"quote": "The ultimate in alien terror", "page_title": "The Thing", "page_bio": "The Thing (film), also known as John Carpenters The Thing, is a 1982 in film science fiction horror film about an Antarctic science base which is infiltrated by a shape-shifting alien that assumes the appearance of the people that it kills. Ostensibly a remake of the 1951 Christian Nyby film The Thing From Another World, Carpenter\u2019s film is more faithful to the original novella \u201cWho Goes There?\u201d by John W. Campbell, Jr.", "page_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The Thing (film)"}